document.title: Hello World
document.summary: I sometimes write about things I'm working on.

body.raw:
This is a test post but I'm working on this new blog site for myself.
I'm really tired right now as it's like 1am but I'm going to try to
finish this up soon.

I'll mostly be covering things I'm working on, thing's I'm learning, and
other things that I find interesting all over the internet. Personally, I'm a
pretty boring person so I don't think I'll have much to say. I'll try to
write more.
